      "role": "user",
      "content": "is there even a point to any of this? like i was reading about the heat death of the universe tonight and it just hit me... everything we do, every single feeling or struggle, it's all just going to be erased anyway. it feels like we're just performing a play for an empty theater. it's exhausting to keep pretending it matters.",
